<p>If you are travelling to Italy for the first time in your life, the best thing for you is to be prepared and know what to expect to experience Italy at the fullest! Whether you are visiting enchanting medieval cities in Tuscany, white sand beaches in Puglia or the natural treasures of the Dolomites, Italy will amaze you for its beauty and magic which you won’t find anywhere else. If you are a conscious consumer and give value to your money, some advice might be helpful in order not to be caught by surprise.</p>

